<body>
<div>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.1 (STRIPS 1-2) JI XUSHENG 4: 74">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-1a.1">簡大王迫[暴]旱，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-1a.2">命龜尹羅貞於大夏.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-1a.3">王自臨卜.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-1a.4">王向日而立，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-1a.5">王汗至帶.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-1a.6">龜尹知</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-1a.7">王之炙於日而病,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-1a.8">蓋榦逾夭(?).</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.2 (STRIPS 2, 8) JI XUSHENG 4: 74">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-2a.1">釐尹知</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-2a.2">王之病，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-2a.3">承龜尹</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-2a.4">速卜高山深溪.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-2a.5">王以問釐尹高：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-2a.6">“不穀燥甚病，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-2a.7">驟夢高山深溪.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.3 (STRIPS 8, 3) JI XUSHENG 4: 74-75">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-3a.1">吾所得地於呂中者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-3a.2">無有名山名溪.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-3a.3">欲祭於楚邦者乎.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-3a.4">當蔽而卜之於大夏.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-3a.5">如孚，將祭之.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.4 (STRIPS 3, 4) JI XUSHENG 4: 75">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-4a.1">釐尹許諾，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-4a.2">蔽而卜之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-4a.3">孚.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-4a.4">釐尹致命於君王：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-4a.5">“既蔽而卜之, 孚.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.5 (STRIPS 4, 5) JI XUSHENG 4: 75">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-5a.1">王曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-5a.2">“如孚，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-5a.3">速祭之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-5a.4">吾燥一病.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-5a.5">釐尹答曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-5a.6">“楚邦有常故，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-5a.7">焉敢殺祭?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-5a.8">以君王之身殺祭，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-5a.9">未嘗有.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.6 (STRIPS 5, 7, 19) JI XUSHENG 4: 75">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-6a.1">王入，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-6a.2">以告安君與陵尹子高：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-6a.3">“向爲私便,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-6a.4">人將笑君.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-6a.5">陵尹, 釐尹皆持其言</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-6a.6">以告太宰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-6a.7">“君聖人且良長子，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-6a.8">將正於君.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.7 (STRIPS 19, 20) JI XUSHENG 4: 75">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-7a.1">太宰謂陵尹：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-7a.2">“君入</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-7a.3">而語僕之言於君王,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-7a.4">君王之燥從今日以瘥.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-7a.5">陵尹與釐尹：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-7a.6">“有故乎?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-7a.7">願聞之.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.8 (STRIPS 21, 6, 22) JI XUSHENG 4: 75">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-8a.1">太宰言：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-8a.2">“君王元君，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-8a.3">不以其身變釐尹之常故；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-8a.4">釐尹爲楚邦之鬼神主，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-8a.5">不敢以君王之身</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-8a.6">變亂鬼神之常故.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-8a.7">夫上帝鬼神高明甚，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-8a.8">將必知之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-8a.9">君王之病將從今日以已.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.9 (STRIPS 22, 23) JI XUSHENG 4: 75">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-9a.1">令尹子林問於太宰子止：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-9a.2">“爲人臣者</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-9a.3">亦有爭乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-9a.4">太宰答曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-9a.5">“君王元君，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-9a.6">君善，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-9a.7">大夫何用爭.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.10 (STRIPS 23, 18) JI XUSHENG 4: 75">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-10a.1">令尹謂太宰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-10a.2">“唯.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-10a.3">必三軍有大事，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-10a.4">邦家以杌捏(?)，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-10a.5">社稷以危(?)歟?</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.11 (STRIPS 18, 17) JI XUSHENG 4: 75-76">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-11a.1">邦家大旱，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-11a.2">因資智於邦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-11a.3">將爲客告.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-11a.4">太宰乃而謂之：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-11a.5">“君皆楚邦之將軍，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-11a.6">作色而言於廷，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-11a.7">王事何 [...]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.12 (STRIPS 17, 9) JI XUSHENG 4: 76">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-12a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-12a.1">王諾，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-12a.2">將鼓</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-12a.3">而涉之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-12a.4">王夢三.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-12a.5">閨未啓，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-12a.6">以告相徙與中余：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-12a.7">“今夕不穀夢若此，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-12a.8">何?”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.13 (STRIPS 9, 10) JI XUSHENG 4: 76">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-13a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-13a.1">相徙、中余答：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-13a.2">“君王當以問太宰晉侯，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-13a.3">彼聖人之子孫.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-13a.4">“將必鼓</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-13a.5">而涉之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-13a.6">此何?”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.14 (STRIPS 10, 11, 12) JI XUSHENG 4: 76">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-14a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-14a.1">太宰進答：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-14a.2">“此所謂之‘旱母’，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-14a.3">帝將命之</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-14a.4">修諸侯之君之不能治者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-14a.5">而刑之以旱.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-14a.6">夫雖毋旱，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-14a.7">而百姓移</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-14a.8">以去邦家.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-14a.9">此爲君者之刑.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.15 (STRIPS 14, 13) JI XUSHENG 4: 76">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-15a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-15a.1">王仰天啕，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-15a.2">而泣謂太宰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-15a.3">“一人不能治政，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-15a.4">而百姓以絕.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-15a.5">後太宰遜.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-15a.6">返進太宰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-15a.7">“我何爲，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-15a.8">歲焉熟?”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JIANDAHANBOHAN 4.18.16 (STRIPS 13, 15) JI XUSHENG 4: 76">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-16a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-16a.1">太宰答：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-16a.2">“如君王修郢郊，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-16a.3">方若然里(?)，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-16a.4">君王毋敢栽介蓋；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-16a.5">相徙、中余與五連小子及寵臣皆屬，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0047_tls_001-16a.6">毋敢執澡箑.”</seg>
                </p>

